<section id="readingText">
	<h1>Writing Task 1</h1>
	<p>You should spend about 20 minutes on this task.</p>
 	<p><b>You are planning a holiday in Scotland. You have been given the name and address of a hotel near the sea and would like some further information.</b></p>
	<p><b>Write a letter to the hotel. Ask for information about the hotel's exact location and facilities. Explain any special requirements you have and ask whether the hotel can accommodate them.</b></p>
	<p>You should write at least 150 words.</p>
	<p>You do&#xA0;<b>NOT</b>&#xA0;need to write your own address.</p>
	<p>Begin your letter as follows:</p>
	<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>
</section>

<section id="body">
<ol id="splitquestionList">
	<li>Who do you have to write to?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t1">a friend</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t2">a relative</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t3">a colleague</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t4">an acquaintance</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t5">a stranger</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>
	  
	<li>What style of letter should you write?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t6">formal</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t7">informal</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>

	<li>What do you have to do in this letter?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t8">make arrangement</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t9">request information</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t10">offer advice</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t11">make a complaint</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t12">provide information</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>	  

	<li>How many points do you have to cover in this letter?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t13">one</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t14">two</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t15">three</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t16">four</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t17">five</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>		  

	<li>Which of the following could you ask about in this letter?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t18">if the hotel has a swimming pool</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t19">when the hotel was established</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t20">how far the hotel is from the town centre</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t21">what the weather will be like in August</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t22">if they provide meals for vegetarians</a></li>
	  </list></li>
